<P>Nearly every Omens spell for every class was just a "cut and paste" job of the previous versions.&nbsp; That means that the reagent cost got cut and pasted right along with the numbers.&nbsp; Given that OoW won't even come out until the end of the summer, there's still plenty of time for them to go back in and actually change some of the information.&nbsp; Some changes to the spells have been made, however peridot cost wasn't one of them.&nbsp; Now, if OoW launches with the reagent costs still on the spells, then we can all have a reason to riot.</P>
