		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<P>Hey Kyth, would you be so kind as to remind rytan that unlimited mod rods were removed from the game, and the mana costs of spells need to be adjusted to reflect that?</P>
<P>PoP spells were finalized while unlimited mod rods were still on the table (hence buffs cost more than older spells, in some cases more on a per effect bases than level 49 spells) </P>
<P>Also, spells like pacification, which were nerfed in effect, but the mana cost was not adjusted.&nbsp;it was never adjusted to reflect its (new) 45 second duration cap... same with older spells in the line. (which were 7.5 minutes duraiton)</P>
<P>For understanding of what im talking about, please compare the following:</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<DIV>Blessing of Faith (39) spell haste 10% cost 200, duration 40min.</DIV>
<DIV>Blessing of Reverence (62) spell haste 10% cost 300, duration 40min.&nbsp; <FONT color=#ff0000>50% mana cost increase no effect change.</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#66ff00>(post PoP spell line)</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Shield of Words&nbsp;(49) 31ac cost 300, duration 1hr 12min<FONT color=#ff0000> </FONT><FONT color=#66ff00>9.677 mana per ac</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Bulwark of Faith (57) 37ac cost 350, duration 1hr 21min <FONT color=#66ff00>9.459 mana per ac</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Ward of Gallantry (61) 54ac cost 425, duration 1hr 21min <FONT color=#66ff00>7.87 mana per ac</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#66ff00>(post PoP spell line)</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Guard of Vie (44) 700 10% rune cost 175, duration 36min <FONT color=#66ff00>4 rune per mana</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Protection of Vie (54) 1200 10% rune cost 250, duration 36min <FONT color=#66ff00>4.8 rune per mana</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Bulwark of Vie (62) 1600 10% rune cost 300, duration 36min <FONT color=#66ff00>5.33 rune per mana</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#66ff00>(post PoP spell line)</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Resolution (44) 16ac, 250hp cost 110, duration 1hr 3min <FONT color=#66ff00>6.875 mana per ac, 2.27 hp per mana</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Heroism (52) 19ac, 450hp cost 140, duration 1hr 12min <FONT color=#ff0000>7.368 mana per ac, </FONT><FONT color=#66ff00>3.21 hp per mana</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Faith (61) 22ac, 520hp cost 200, duration 1hr 12min <FONT color=#ff0000>9.09 mana per ac, 2.6 hp per mana</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Symbol of Naltron (44) 525hp cost 315, duration 54min <FONT color=#66ff00>1.66 hp per mana</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Symbol of Marzin (54) 700hp cost 350, duration 1hr 3min <FONT color=#66ff00>2 hp per mana</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Symbol of Kazaad (61) 910hp cost 600, duration 1hr 3min <FONT color=#ff0000>1.52 hp per mana</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Naltron's Mark (58) 525hp cost 500, duration 54min <FONT color=#66ff00>1.05 to 6.3 hp per mana</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Marzin's Mark (60) 725hp cost 575, duration 1hr 23min <FONT color=#66ff00>1.26 to 7.56 hp per mana</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Kazad's Mark (63) 910hp cost 1800, duration 1hr 3min <FONT color=#ff0000>.50 to 3.03 hp per mana</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Temprence (44) 800hp 48ac cost 550, duration 1hr 40min <FONT color=#66ff00>1.45 hp per mana, 11.45 mana per ac</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Aegolism (60) 1100hp 54ac cost 750, duration 2hr 30min <FONT color=#66ff00>1.46 hp per mana,&nbsp;</FONT><FONT color=#ff0000>13.88 mana per ac</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Virtue (62) 1405hp 72ac cost 1000, duration 2hr 30min <FONT color=#ff0000>1.40 hp per mana, 13.88 mana per ac</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Blessing of Temprence (49) 800hp 48ac cost 1650. duration 1hr 40min <FONT color=#66ff00>.48 to 2.90 hp per mana, 34.37 to 5.72 mana per ac</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Blessing of Ageolism (60) 1150hp 60ac cost 2000, duration 2hr 30min <FONT color=#66ff00>.57 to 3.45 hp per mana, 33.33 to 5.55 mana per ac</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Hand of Virtue (65) 1405hp 72ac cost 2500, duration 2hr 30min <FONT color=#ff0000>.56 to 3.37 hp per mana, 34.72 to 5.78 mana per ac</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Pacify (39) 1/55 pac, 100mana 45 seconds, was 7.5 minutes <FONT color=#66ff00>100 mana per target</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Wake of Tranquility (55)&nbsp;1/60 4 target, 300mana 45 seconds, was 7.5 minutes <FONT color=#66ff00>as low as 75 mana per target</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>Pacificiation (65) 1/65 350mana 45 seconds, was 7.5 minutes <FONT color=#ff0000>went from quad for 300 to single for 350?</FONT></DIV>
